dcterms:description: WojoodF ine is a fine-grained Arabic NER dataset that includes subtypes of entities, enhancing the original Wojood corpus. It contains approximately 550k tokens and is annotated with 51 entity types and subtypes.
dcterms:title: WojoodF ine

dcterms:description: WojoodGaza is a dataset specifically curated for the Open-Track NER subtask related to the Israeli War on Gaza. It includes 60k tokens collected from various news domains and is annotated with fine-grained named entities.
dcterms:title: WojoodGaza
